The Presidential candidate of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP), Atiku Abubakar, on Wednesday congratulated Asiwaju Bola Tinubu on emerging the presidential candidate of the ruling All Progressives Congress (APC) at the party’s national convention in Abuja.
Atiku on his official Twitter handle, Atiku Abubakar @atiku commended Tinubu for his tenacity to avail in the hard-fought contest to secure the APC presidential ticket.
Atiku in his tweet wrote: “Congratulations, @officialABAT, on your emergence as your party’s presidential candidate.
“It has been a hard-fought contest, but that you prevailed confirms your tenacity.”
Tinubu had congratulated Atiku when he won the PDP presidential ticket at the national convention in Abuja.

